      • addInterest

        public void addInterest(java.lang.String type,
               java.lang.String description)
                 throws JSONException,
                        ClientProtocolException,
                        java.io.IOException
        this class adds the newly added interest using type_interest and description to your profile. The Http Client sends an HTTP POST request to the API to create a new interest. The API sends information which is stored in Android via JSON to the webserver. Here new interests belonged to the user are created.
